text: Yujiro Imano is a male former international table tennis player from Japan. ==Table tennis career== He won a bronze medal at the 1971 World Table Tennis Championships with Katsuyuki Abe and another bronze in the men's team event at the 1973 World Table Tennis Championships. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:Japanese male table tennis players Category:Living people Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Yujiro Imano
